               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra ʾIyasus “Miracles of Jesus” (fols. 2ra-52vb)&#xD; I-1)
                     ʾƎsaggǝd la-malakotǝka... “I worship Thy Godhead…” (fols. 2ra-4rb)&#xD; I-2)
                     Introduction (fols. 5ra-16rb)&#xD; - On John the Evangelist as the author of
                     the book; on the creation and the fall of the angels (fols. 5ra-10ra)&#xD; -
                     Story of the family of Adam (fols. 10ra-16rb)&#xD; I-3) Taʾāmra ʾIyasus
                     “Miracles of Jesus”: 15 miracles (fols. 16rb-52vb), incomplete [continuation of
                     the text is in AMM-006]&#xD; &#xD; Additio 1.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
